Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Con đi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Đội phó - Kogure Kiminobu]\N[Lớp 12 - 178cm]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Biệt danh: Bốn Mắt]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure, không ai phòng thủ cả, mau ném đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Vào rồi, vào rồi.
